{"id":18,"date":"2023-05-18T11:34:10","date_gmt":"2023-05-18T11:34:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/?page_id=18"},"modified":"2023-10-12T16:30:21","modified_gmt":"2023-10-12T16:30:21","slug":"faq","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/faq\/","title":{"rendered":"Popular Questions"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section alignfull alignfull\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__wrapper getwid-padding-tablet-top-large getwid-padding-tablet-bottom-large\" style=\"padding-top:175px;padding-bottom:140px\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background-holder\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__background has-background has-color-4-background-color\"><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__foreground\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__content\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-section__inner-content\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-style-wide-space is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion\" data-active-element=\"none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">How can I rent a yacht or boat from your website?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Renting a yacht or boat from our website is easy. Simply visit our homepage and browse our selection of available yachts and boats. Once you&#8217;ve found the one you want, click on the &#8220;Rent Now&#8221; button and follow the booking process. Provide the necessary details, select your desired rental duration, and finalize the reservation.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Are there any requirements to rent a yacht or boat?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Yes, to rent a yacht or boat from our website, you must be at least 18 years old and possess a valid government-issued identification document. Depending on the size and type of vessel, you may also need to provide proof of boating experience or certification. Please review the specific requirements mentioned in the boat listings.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">How long can I rent a yacht or boat for?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>We offer flexible rental durations to suit your needs. You can rent a yacht or boat for a half-day, full day, or even multiple days, depending on availability. During the booking process, you can select your preferred rental duration and check the availability of the vessel.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion\" data-active-element=\"none\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Are fuel costs included in the rental price?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Fuel costs are typically not included in the rental price. You will be responsible for fuel expenses during your rental period. The yacht or boat will be provided to you with a full tank, and you should refuel it before returning it to the designated location.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">Can I cancel or modify my yacht or boat reservation?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>Yes, you can cancel or modify your reservation, subject to our cancellation and modification policy. The ability to do so and any associated fees will depend on the timing and terms of cancellation or modification. We recommend reviewing the specific details during the booking process or contacting our customer support for assistance.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-wrapper\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header\"><a href=\"#\"><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__header-title\">What happens if there is inclement weather during my rental period?<\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-active\"><i class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__icon is-passive\"><i class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content-wrapper\"><div class=\"wp-block-getwid-accordion__content\">\n<p>If there is inclement weather that makes it unsafe or impossible to go out on the water, we will work with you to reschedule your rental or provide a refund, depending on the circumstances. Your safety is our top priority, and we will consider weather conditions when making rental decisions. Please contact our customer support team in such situations.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":108,"featured_media":109,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"template-canvas-header-page.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/18"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/108"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/18\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4133,"href":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/lorenty-yacht\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/18\/revisions\